        "TileImage": "$($repository b6402e40-06e7-46b6-b082-54c228010b71).Image",
        "Description": "哈梅特舒心 The Harmette Comfort\r关卡目标：\r*先前关卡内容已变更\r*穿着潜水教练服装，消灭克里斯蒂·霍华兹，索菲亚·贝蒂，佐伊·卡拉韦拉，辛迪·麦肯罗和贝赞尼·费德勒\r*从摩托艇撤离\r*不得被发现，弹无虚发和枪枪爆头\rThe Targets:\r*The previous contents are changed now\r*Eliminate Christie Howards,Sofia Beti,Zoe Caravella,Cindy McEnroe and Bethany Fiedler when you disguise as the diving coach\r*Extract by the motorboat\r*No spotted,all shot on targets and must be headshot",
